node.text:
@dr.zelana suggests doing these things every day to improve your emotional well-being: 

1. Start your day with water before all else
2. Step outside for fresh air daily
3. Eat sitting down 
4. Connect with a friend
5. Create a consistent bedtime ritual 

Will you be incorporating these practices into your day? Let me know in the comments.

node.text:
Don't bug out! Cicada season is approaching in many states, so @marascampo and I did a quick Q&A with entomologist, Mike Deutsch ⬇️ 

➡️ How often do cicadas appear? 

➡️ How long are cicadas around for?

➡️ Are cicadas dangerous? 

➡️ Why do cicadas make so much noise!?

➡️ Is there anything I can do to repel cicadas? 

For more on this topic, plus travel + safety tips from @thepointsguy, be sure to watch #TheDrOzShow tomorrow. 
.
.
.
#Summer #Bugs #Cicadas #CicadaSeason #BugsLife

node.text: SEASON 13 IS HERE! Happy premiere today, everyone. We’re back in the studio with  @howiemandel; plus, all season long on #TheDrOzShow we’re going to show you how to reset and reconnect. Click my link in bio to find your local listings and be sure to tune in today. #Season13 #Lucky13

node.text: We’re kicking off lucky season 13 of #TheDrOzShow tomorrow! Get ready to reset and reconnect. Check your local listings on doctoroz.com and enjoy this walk down memory lane. #Lucky13 #Season13 #DrOz

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Dr. Oz on September 12, 2021 tagging @ooh_liver, and @ochsorchard. May be an image of 2 people, people standing, fruit and outdoors.

node.text:
Oliver escaped med school to go apple picking with me this morning (how lucky am I!). 

You know what they say… an apple a day keeps the doctor away! 
•
•
•
#applepicking #applepickingseason #fatherson #ochsorchard
